properties.description: Create Place Of Service Dim Tables.

content.query:
DROP TABLE [dbo].[PlaceOfServiceDim] ;

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[PlaceOfServiceDim]
( 
	[PlaceOfServiceKey] [int]  NOT NULL,
	[PlaceOfServiceEpicId] [nvarchar](50)  NULL,
	[Name] [nvarchar](200)  NULL,
	[DisplayName] [nvarchar](300)  NULL,
	[Type] [nvarchar](300)  NULL,
	[FacilityType] [nvarchar](300)  NULL,
	[LocationCcn] [nvarchar](300)  NULL,
	[PhoneNumber] [nvarchar](100)  NULL,
	[Address] [nvarchar](300)  NULL,
	[City] [nvarchar](100)  NULL,
	[StateOrProvince] [nvarchar](100)  NULL,
	[PostalCode] [nvarchar](25)  NULL,
	[County] [nvarchar](25)  NULL,
	[Country] [nvarchar](25)  NULL,
	[EmailAddress] [nvarchar](100)  NULL,
	[WebAddress] [nvarchar](100)  NULL,
	[CreatedTimeStamp] [datetime]  NULL,
	[UpdatedTimeStamp] [datetime]  NULL,
	[MD5Hash] [nvarchar](500)  NULL
)
WITH
(
	DISTRIBUTION = HASH ( [PlaceOfServiceKey] ),
	CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)
GO ;


CREATE TABLE [dbo].[PlaceOfServiceDim_IdLookup](
[PlaceOfServiceKey] [int] IDENTITY(1, 1) NOT NULL,
[Id] [varchar](50) NOT NULL,
[IdType] [varchar](50) NULL,
[CreatedTimeStamp] [datetime]  NULL,
[UpdatedTimeStamp] [datetime]  NULL
)
